  "description": "This Texture Pack Dynamic changes the actual texture and model of your tools based on the specific enchantments applied to them, for now its just the pickaxes.",
  "body": "<br>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/522ec22674b9b1faf6e8e97bc3203deda9161638.png\"\n    alt=\"Drigo Enchanted Tools Title\"\n    width=\"850\">\n</p>\n\n<br>\n\n<hr>\n\n<br>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/17aeebc13d1a3219e7e518d7a7f22a49446d7a4a_0.webp\"\n    alt=\"Description\"\n    style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto;\">\n</p>\n\n<br>\n\n<p align=\"center\">This Texture Pack Dynamic changes the actual texture and model of your tools based on the specific enchantments applied to them. For now its just all the Pickaxes, but i will makr this changes to all Tools</p>\n\n<h1></h1>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b1ac43139c3b5953fcc3eaada104493993aec9c2.jpeg\"\n    alt=\"Enchanted Tools Image 1\"\n    style=\"width: 1920px; height: 1080px;\">\n</p>\n\n<h1></h1>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/3e0e4ce2526ee86567dbb7916b15878970366ad2.jpeg\"\n    alt=\"Enchanted Tools Image 2\"\n    style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto;\">\n</p>\n\n<h1></h1>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/f19e6d2865800e26e519f5ef0d5eef9017783dfe.jpeg\"\n    alt=\"Enchanted Tools Image 3\"\n    style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto;\">\n</p>\n\n<h1></h1>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/daadb0edb8936d73fd6aaa58ac24c94b686c81bb.jpeg\"\n    alt=\"Enchanted Tools Image 4\"\n    style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto;\">\n</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img \n    src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a84a822e69f5e42576ea0631129332b714a27a0a_0.webp\"\n    alt=\"LINKS\"\n    width=\"170\">\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/drigo/projects\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-wixmp-ed30a86b8c4ca887773594c2.wixmp.com%2Ff%2F159648c2-8de7-4641-a129-8d8c2d06bd9c%2Fdee1zh0-f9e45f11-8ff2-4032-8215-72e54c647a9f.png%3Ftoken%3DeyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9..fjO_Mm_jiHcc42PG-UJYYuQBR8JPs7bX9NCjPIfOD6g&n=-1\" width=\"70\" alt=\"CurseForge\">\n  </a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"https://www.planetminecraft.com/member/drigo/\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Flh7-rt.googleusercontent.com%2Fdocsz%2FAD_4nXdNMHQhEsV5eId8RgQzyG0GNxBl2Gpb7OQ0y300mcCgU03FMk2DHKoVTJtGA7DA0-KZUEbkNDBAB14my7CItBw_pz5hwycDcHVS7IUNMNY4n7ATuEpK1MDdtL34KEh7Vd3lQiFl%3Fkey%3DTs9sQSSfeNWwwKd7mSkTE4H1&n=-1\" width=\"70\" alt=\"PlanetMinecraft\">\n  </a>\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Drigo\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn2.steamgriddb.com/icon/46bbc4a56de136ad319e59e37ef55644/32/256x256.png\" width=\"70\" alt=\"Modrinth\">\n  &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/drigo_\" target=\"_blank\">\n    <img src=\"https://meta-q.cdn.bubble.io/f1718310734171x219118565666597060/64f1a9ddd0246590df69e9ef_ko-fi_logo_02.png\" width=\"70\" alt=\"Ko-fi\">\n  </a>\n</p>",
